[Crown Agents is an international development company that partners with governments, aid agencies, NGOs and companies in nearly 100 countries. They help countries grow their economies, strengthen their health systems, and improve financial management. This report points out the difficulties of sending health care workers to West Africa to fight Ebola. - Mod.LK]

